    <item>
      <title>Google 強調 AI 搜尋功能讓網頁獲得更高品質點擊觀看行為、連結查詢數量增加，但未提供數據佐證</title>
      <description>&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;針對市場質疑科技業者大幅推廣 AI 應用服務，進而造成許多內容網站、部落格等流量&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://mashdigi.com/google-is-again-caught-up-in-eu-antitrust-storm-ai-overviews-infringement-dispute-sparks-dissatisfaction-in-news-publishing-industry/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:大幅減少;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;大幅減少&lt;/a&gt;，市調機構皮尤研究中心 (Pew Research Center) 製作&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2025/07/22/google-users-are-less-likely-to-click-on-links-when-an-ai-summary-appears-in-the-results/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:研究報告;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;研究報告&lt;/a&gt;，指出 Google 搜尋加入&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://mashdigi.com/?s=AI+Overviews" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:AI Overviews 功能;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;AI Overviews 功能&lt;/a&gt;後，對整體網站流量帶來明顯衝擊。不過，Google 搜尋業務負責人 Liz Reid&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://blog.google/products/search/ai-search-driving-more-queries-higher-quality-clicks/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:透過官方部落格回應;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;透過官方部落格回應&lt;/a&gt;，表示搜尋導向網站的流量「相對穩定」，同時使用者點擊的「品質更高」，試圖為外界對 AI 功能可能損害內容生態的疑慮提出不同觀點。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class="mb-module-gap"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto w-fit"&gt;&lt;img alt="Google 強調 AI 搜尋功能讓網頁獲得更高品質點擊觀看行為、連結查詢數量增加，但未提供數據佐證" class="rounded-lg" loading="lazy" height="515" src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AeB3xo7EFIsKtwZ10sA0oA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUxNQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-08/a1b45c90-73a7-11f0-b74f-39767a981297" width="960" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;figcaption class="text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere" style="max-width:960px"&gt;Google 強調 AI 搜尋功能讓網頁獲得更高品質點擊觀看行為、連結查詢數量增加，但未提供數據佐證&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;Liz Reid 在部落格中表示，AI Overviews 功能推出後，使用者的搜尋行為變得更加頻繁，查詢內容也趨於複雜與多樣化，進一步帶動整體點擊次數與搜尋品質的提升，強調人們透過 AI Overviews 功能取得解答後，實際上會提出</description>
      <link>https://tw.news.yahoo.com/google-emphasized-that-its-ai-search-function-has-led-to-higher-quality-click-through-rates-and-an-increase-in-link-queries-but-did-not-provide-data-to-support-this-160129014.html</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/google-emphasized-that-its-ai-search-function-has-led-to-higher-quality-click-through-rates-and-an-increase-in-link-queries-but-did-not-provide-data-to-support-this-160129014.html</guid>
